title: Opie & Jim Norton OCT 23 2015 Fri.mp3
description:
There was no show Thursday 22nd.


Opie & Jim Norton OCT 23 2015 Fri (02:51:32)

On Today's Show:

VIC HENLEY, MIKE BOCCHETTI, NEIL deGRASSE TYSON.

The show starts with VIC HENLEY in studio.
We find out that Erock was promoted to Channel runner. Obscure references talk. Soccer player discussion. Jim Breuer's video for the NL Champion Mets & related stories. Some political talk.
Conjoined twins, Chang Eng Bunker discussion.
Opie brings up a Neil deGrasse tyson thing he saw which leads into some science stories & What costumes not to wear for Halloween back to science talk.
MIKE BOCCHETTI in studio.
Questions Mike plans on asking Neil deGrasse tyson. Mike reveals his past lives & thoughts on Heaven, Halloween, Politics & some other topics.
Jeb Bush thinks Supergirl is hot clip.
Back to Mike's past lives fun.
Drunk Eagles Fan Gives a Terrible Pre-game Rally Speech.
Various news clips & discussion.
NEIL deGRASSE TYSON in studio.
Everything they said they were going to ask Neil earlier, they asked & more.
(AFTER SHOW) Some fun during the live commercial reads
